## Ubuntu Install

Start by navigating to the [Ubuntu Website](https://ubuntu.com/) and then going to **Products** -> **Unbuntu OS** -> **Unbuntu Desktop**

<a href="https://ibb.co/7vt3YHk"><img src="https://i.ibb.co/rk2B7gd/Ubuntu-Tutorial-1.png" alt="Ubuntu-Tutorial-1" border="0"></a>

Once there click the download button and download the newest LTS version of Ubuntu.  
Select a folder that you will remember the location of because we need this in the next step.  

See the **[Setup](https://github.com/Daboulch/VMware-Ubuntu-Tutorial/blob/main/Setup)** page next!
